# Valuate Addon Development

This directory contains GitHub-specific files for the Valuate WoW addon project.

## Repository Setup

To push this repository to GitHub:

1. Create a new repository on GitHub (don't initialize with README, .gitignore, or license)

2. Add the remote:
   ```bash
   git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/Valuate.git
   ```

3. Push to GitHub:
   ```bash
   git branch -M main
   git push -u origin main
   ```
